OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The BBC's iPlayer streaming service is 
OL,6, to end downloads for users who watch on
OL,7, desktop or laptop computers.           
OL,9,FProgrammes will still be available to  
OL,10,Fdownload on tablets and phones via the 
OL,11,Fmobile iPlayer app.                    
OL,13,FCurrently viewers on PCs and Macs can  
OL,14,Fsave programmes via the iPlayer        
OL,15,FDownloads app, but that will be closed.
OL,17,FThe changes were "due to the low number
OL,18,Fof people using it and the cost        
OL,19,Frequired to keep it going" the BBC     
OL,20,Fsaid.                                  
